{"tid":1465802,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反思一下，請大家入黎，盡快討論對策","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:38.000Z","uid":287745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49ae26ccf1595c99c3e0febc0893da71858bf478","tid":1465802,"uid":287745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"首先，對於前線任何行動都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係但係，我必須要講，鬼係捉唔完，真係捉捉完隻鬼就算啦，搞一隻鬼搞到幾個鍾，仲點做其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家呢家不如討論下應該點處理啲鬼，有個共識，捉完就放埋一二邊咪算，一隻鬼搞到情緒咁激帳，跟著又罵人地左膠、大愛、道德，咁樣就分化左。<br />\n<br />\n大家要兵貴神速，快啲諗下應該點應對對手嘅放鬼挑鬼。"},{"pid":"83947e8b76cc262722b566dad3ace3c99b1b5d2f","tid":1465802,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b94a11c958aaa68fe3fdcbcc8e1bfe76d75e2469","tid":1465802,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"反思good 保持自己頭腦清晰先係重中之重"},{"pid":"901335133204f329c507a5815c74eaf76e0f1b55","tid":1465802,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"趕佢出去，但過程中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7f6e55ca64fa855503dff6e694a3faaddca14e","tid":1465802,"uid":238343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"鬼一定要捉，餵佢食屎就最好！"},{"pid":"378ea007c03d4e8f2f1ebb6535435eee6efc94b3","tid":1465802,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"你咪放佢走囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6c5b39603ee3fd57fa8b335e938e24e947f4bb","tid":1465802,"uid":287745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"一隻鬼，全版都係講鬼講鬼，講啦唔好捉唔好捉，捉鬼絕對唔會係最好嘅應對方法，但絕對不可不防，大家快啲討論!!!<b